Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.76,0:00:19.13,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\pos(320,38)\c&HFF00FF&}Piercing through the Macro sky,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.45,0:00:24.98,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\pos(320,38)\c&HFF00FF&}a thunderbolt strikes the Earth{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.18,0:00:30.73,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\pos(320,38)\c&HFF00FF&}To awaken us, the young mankind,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.86,0:00:36.74,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\pos(320,38)\c&HFF00FF&}the Light struck{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.13,0:00:42.88,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\pos(320,38)\c&HFF00FF&}Macross! Macross!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.18,0:00:48.74,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,, {\b1\pos(320,38)\c&HFF00FF&}The brave youths who arise{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.89,0:00:52.91,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,, {\b1\pos(320,38)\c&HFF00FF&}and fight to protect their loved ones{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.06,0:00:58.08,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\pos(320,38)\c&HFF00FF&}Will set out on their journey\Nas the war rages on.{\b0}
