Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.01,0:01:24.14,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&\pos(320,38}Macross!{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:36.75,signM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FF00&\pos(76,145)}BYE-BYE MARS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.62,0:02:00.75,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Life signs: negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.93,0:02:03.11,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Energy readings: negative.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.29,0:02:05.08,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm. An abandoned base...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:07.85,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We have reached the friendly\Nforces rendezvous point!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.63,0:02:11.31,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Britai, which forces\Nshall we be meeting up with?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.21,0:02:16.19,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The 109th Branch of the\Nmain Bodol Fleet,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.64,0:02:18.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,7th Sector Armored Division.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.60,0:02:22.37,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that would be... \NSurely you don't mean...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.37,0:02:24.81,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kamujin Kravshera's group?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:27.04,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well done as always, my Archivist.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:30.18,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't!\NAren't you aware of his battle record?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.04,0:02:33.72,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,During Operation Mona, he became\Nintoxicated and started a firefight,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:36.05,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,killing or wounding nearly everyone on board!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.05,0:02:39.43,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, while he killed every\Nlast enemy in the Isulis Sector,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.46,0:02:42.64,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,he destroyed two friendly divisions\Nin the process!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:44.46,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know what they call him now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.61,0:02:46.75,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"Kamujin the Ally Killer," you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:49.93,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Friendly forces are de-folding!\NTh... They're too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.22,0:03:10.36,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What did I tell you?\NThat damned Kamujin!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.43,0:03:13.39,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's always this way with him.\NI wash my hands of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.31,0:03:21.05,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kamujin Kravshera, 7th Sector\nArmored Division, reporting for duty, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.42,0:03:28.10,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We hit four ships.\NI win the bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:30.87,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That booze ration is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.20,0:03:34.17,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it, you fool!\NThe commander can hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:36.18,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry 'bout that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.62,0:03:40.60,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Kamujin! Remember this, and remember it well:\NI will not tolerate any reckless behavior!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.68,0:03:43.79,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've had to wait six {\i1}taarms{\i0} for this,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.79,0:03:47.56,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,so don't throw away your\Nchance to get back into combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:49.86,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do we have to do, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:51.18,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.70,0:03:54.04,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's an abandoned base on the seventh\Nplanet of this system.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.07,0:03:56.24,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You are going to the lure the\Nenemy ship toward it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.29,0:03:59.81,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By that time, you will have planted gravity\Nmines around the base's perimeter,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.85,0:04:01.99,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,preventing the enemy from escaping,\Nbut capturing them alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.28,0:04:04.39,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Enemies closing in from 3 o'clock, mark 60!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.72,0:04:25.24,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Change course!\NAD down 20!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:25.88,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.62,0:04:32.37,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skull Squadron! Intercept enemy craft\Ninbound from 5 o'clock, mark 15!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.73,0:04:34.27,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skull Leader, roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.52,0:05:00.90,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is retreating.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:04.65,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like that's it for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.96,0:05:07.28,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All units, break off attack and return to ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:10.07,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They've been attacking us non-stop\Nfor the last three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:11.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Persistent, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.85,0:05:14.60,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Each time they attack, we're driven\Nfurther off course from Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:15.62,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No {\i1}way!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.08,0:05:26.56,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?\NTired?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.79,0:05:28.62,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, this has been happening every day now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:32.51,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think they'll be back for a while,\Nso why don't you go into town and relax?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.52,0:05:38.26,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a message from the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.36,0:05:42.41,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, we were attacked a force of\N120 enemy units,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:48.34,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,but the 1st, 4th and 7th Valkyrie groups\Nintercepted and destroyed them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.04,0:05:54.38,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our forces took little damage,\Nand the Macross remains on course.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.47,0:05:55.58,intercom paging,,0000,0000,0000,,That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.22,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.\NHow are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:58.53,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Minmay... \NIs school over already?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.84,0:06:01.60,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.\NThey canceled it because of the attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.09,0:06:05.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?\NYou look upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.38,0:06:07.98,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing. But you heard the announcement\Njust now, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.38,0:06:11.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh, we destroyed all the\Nenemy fighters, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.23,0:06:13.62,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It was all lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:17.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't get even half of them,\Nand we lost a lot of men out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.13,0:06:21.45,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Really...\NWell, there's nothing we can do about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.48,0:06:23.80,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never get anywhere in this war\Nif we're depressed all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.40,0:06:25.96,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, let's go get some tea or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:52.36,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I'm having a birthday party on\NOctober 10, so come, okay?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.84,0:06:55.36,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your birthday's next week, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:56.71,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.11,0:07:03.69,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It appears to be an automatic telemetry signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.65,0:07:06.89,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's originating from Mars Base Salla.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.24,0:07:11.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But Salla should be abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:18.10,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Their garrison was attacked and wiped out\Nby anti-UN Forces while {\i1}en route{\i0} home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:22.05,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Could someone have remained at the base?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.27,0:07:23.51,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.67,0:07:28.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However, Salla is extremely large, and there\Nshould still be a lot of supplies there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:30.53,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damage report.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:32.38,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're still running smoothly, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:35.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How far off course from Earth have we gotten?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.95,0:07:38.49,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sixteen degrees toward Mars, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.66,0:07:42.35,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So going to Mars wouldn't put us\Nthat far out of our way...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.70,0:07:44.68,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a good opportunity\Nto resupply ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:47.87,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Alter our heading.\NSet course for Mars!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.42,0:08:13.56,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"That big red planet there is Mars.\NThat's where I'm going next week."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.42,0:08:17.97,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"So it's for sure, 2nd Lieutenant Riber?\NYou're going to Mars?"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:22.34,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"That's right. After all those applications,\NI've finally been approved."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:26.33,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I'm sure your dad pulled a lot\Nof strings to help me out as well."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.82,0:08:29.72,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"No, not at all...\NBut I'm happy for you."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.57,0:08:34.33,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I may be a soldier, but I'm just\Nno good at fighting."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.91,0:08:36.73,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I'm a lot more suited to being\Non an observation base."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:38.63,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Well..."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:42.53,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Whoops, don't go telling your dad that."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:45.32,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Of course I won't!\NI won't tell anyone!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.53,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"But this means we can't see\Neach other anymore."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.16,0:08:52.65,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"It won't be long before anyone\Nwill be able to go to Mars."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:57.47,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"That's it! I'll join the military,\Ntoo, and go to Mars!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.16,0:09:00.38,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"I hope you can get there soon."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:08.46,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Don't keep me waiting."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.35,0:09:10.73,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Take care of yourself!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.48,0:09:28.89,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hayase...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.43,0:09:30.11,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hayase!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.47,0:09:33.42,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Send out a Cat's Eye recon plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:34.44,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A... Aye, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.92,0:09:45.12,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing on the base or in\Nthe surrounding area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:49.65,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is Gerao in the scout Reguld\Nto Captain Kamujin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.48,0:09:52.46,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A recon unit is headed your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.81,0:10:14.22,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy ship is descending.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.27,0:10:15.60,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's down.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.02,0:10:20.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The ship has landed, but it's outside\Nthe range of our gravity mines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.89,0:10:24.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It won't be long before the\Nenemy moves closer to the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.44,0:10:27.32,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When they do, they'll come into\Nrange of the gravity mines,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.37,0:10:29.80,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and then they'll never lift off again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:56.72,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Destroid forces, fan out and secure the supplies!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.79,0:10:59.01,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Valkyrie units, guard the transport vehicles!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.94,0:11:01.50,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The base perimeter is all clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:03.17,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're moving in to guard the transports.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.01,0:11:18.71,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Supply transport is underway.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.84,0:11:20.50,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Move the Macross closer to the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.36,0:11:21.93,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:34.72,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, that's it...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.62,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The moment you step into our trap,\Nit's time for battle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.33,0:11:41.45,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sir, I'd like permission to go to the base as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.00,0:11:42.72,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:46.27,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want to find out what started that transmission.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.28,0:11:48.15,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.60,0:11:49.37,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFFFFFF&}What if there are some survivors?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:56.66,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cover her position, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:11:59.32,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.\NPermission granted.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.87,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy ship is now within\Nrange of the gravity mines.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.29,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to be patient a little while longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.44,0:12:32.67,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sempai, um, do you mind if I take\Nsome leave next week?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.06,0:12:35.67,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah, everyone in our squadron\Nwants leave next week.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:40.67,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They all got invitations to Little Miss\NMinmay's birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.19,0:12:42.36,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Myself included!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.66,0:12:45.57,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who's out there doing all this\Nunnecessary chatting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.61,0:12:47.03,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh-ho, Claudia!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.70,0:12:49.42,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What, it's not the old lady as usual?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.93,0:12:53.20,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The person you're referring to is currently\Ndriving past your feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:29.38,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This was activated only recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.46,0:13:37.46,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But how?\NThis place is abandoned.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.61,0:13:46.56,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gerao, how much longer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.11,0:13:50.62,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Energy levels are at 70%.\NIt won't be long now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.83,0:13:52.57,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is becoming irritating...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:55.26,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, I can't take it anymore!\NI'm going on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.33,0:13:56.20,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:03.51,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!\NEven I'm being patient, but you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:16.52,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!\NNobody disobeys me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.98,0:14:19.69,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, everyone listen up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.69,0:14:21.21,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There will be no more stunts like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.72,0:14:24.18,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,An abnormal tremor has been detected\Nin the mountain ravines.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.98,0:14:26.54,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like an explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.00,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,An explosion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.22,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Send the Cat's Eye out there at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:35.96,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cat's Eye 207, please investigate the area\N15 kilometers out at 11 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:38.77,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cat's Eye 207, roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:46.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have they noticed us...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.25,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How much longer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:49.50,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Another ten percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:50.59,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.62,0:14:54.51,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Cat's Eye data analysis complete.\NI'll put it on screen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.23,0:14:59.93,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?\N It's a huge force of battle pods!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:03.52,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it looks to be at least a thousand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Claudia!\NPut the ship on battle alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.04,0:15:11.07,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All hands, battle stations!\NI repeat, all hands, battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.42,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, will we be able to\Nrepel them all?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.91,0:15:16.47,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible, there are just too many.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.91,0:15:18.42,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lift off at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:19.98,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.35,0:15:22.56,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Gravity control system, stand by!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.73,0:15:30.75,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're not rising!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.82,0:15:32.15,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is it broken again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:35.72,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir, the system's functioning properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.65,0:15:39.37,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on! There's something buried\Ndeep underground!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:43.04,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it's interfering with the\NMacross's gravity control system!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.10,0:15:44.21,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.81,0:15:45.99,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A trap...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.81,0:15:47.81,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Engines, all stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:51.14,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,NOW...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.19,0:15:52.13,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.23,0:15:56.20,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kamujin, the gravity mines are\Nnow running at full effectiveness.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:58.31,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Our prey is caught firmly in its trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:01.46,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Good! All right you bastards,\Nmove out and attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:21.49,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A massive enemy assault force is\Nclosing on us at high speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.57,0:16:22.27,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,They've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.31,0:16:24.98,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Defense forces are already moving to intercept.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.15,0:16:27.02,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But if we don't do\Nsomething fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:31.08,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Vanessa, show me the buried trap again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.37,0:16:32.17,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aye, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.77,0:16:34.53,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Three kilometers below\Nground, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.48,0:16:39.45,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If it's that far underground, there's no way\Nfor the Macross to disable it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.46,0:16:42.81,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we just use the main rockets to lift off?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.99,0:16:47.21,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Dummy! The main rockets were damaged in\Nbattle three days ago, so we can't use them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.51,0:16:50.75,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy assault force is\Nentering the red zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.47,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we can't take off, we're going\Nto make a really easy target.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:55.97,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The target can't fly, so let's get rid of\Nsome of these pesky little ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:57.35,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,CHARGE!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:10.38,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!\NCome and get me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.74,0:17:15.58,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Destroid groups 6, 8, and 17 are destroyed.\NThe rest are heavily damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.68,0:17:18.71,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. We may be able to disable\Nthat trap after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.95,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But how if it's underground?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.68,0:17:25.54,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The reactor! Salla's reactor is located\Ndeep beneath the base.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.96,0:17:27.77,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we can blow it up...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.28,0:17:29.58,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One moment, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:34.83,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like it could work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.22,0:17:37.31,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, begin the operation at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.83,0:17:40.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Have Hayase activate the reactor!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.75,0:17:41.45,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.64,0:17:43.77,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Blow it up?\NThe base?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:47.74,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to put the base's reactor\Ninto overload so we can destroy
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:50.24,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,the devices that are neutralizing\Nour gravity control system.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.64,0:17:53.54,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.22,0:17:56.87,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do this for the 70,000 people we\Nhave on board the Macross!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:02.04,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think she can do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:03.67,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Contact Focker!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.86,0:18:06.15,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!\NI'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:13.69,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It can't be anyone else.\NI'll... I'll do it myself!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:42.32,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Reactor is overloading!\NDanger! Danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:47.29,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Safety systems are disengaged. Status red!\NReactor entering critical cascade!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:49.04,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen minutes until detonation!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.09,0:18:51.05,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All personnel, evacuate!\NAll personnel, evacuate!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:53.70,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like she's done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.37,0:18:56.75,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Order the Destroid groups to pull back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:00.14,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And try to lure the enemy to the base,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.21,0:19:02.77,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,so we can take some of them\Nout while we're at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.10,0:19:03.58,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:15.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What? They're falling back already?\NThose toothless cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.49,0:19:19.13,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Victory is mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.49,0:19:22.62,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,1st Lieutenant Hayase, get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.29,0:19:25.20,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Forgive me, Lt. Riber...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.25,0:19:31.04,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Alert! Engaging bulkheads to contain\Nalpha-particle outflow!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:44.47,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Riber...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:53.24,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Eight minutes to detonation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.33,0:20:04.51,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Riber, I finally made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:06.39,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,1st Lieutenant Hayase, please come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:10.45,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Misa! Misa, come in! Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.67,0:20:13.26,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Send someone in there to get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:17.33,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,1st Lt. Hayase is still inside the building,\Nand we have to rescue her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.88,0:20:19.63,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hikaru, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.09,0:20:21.13,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?\NWhy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:24.11,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This time, the object is to save someone's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:25.80,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I figured that would be easier for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:29.40,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not too crazy about having to\Nsave 1st Lt. Hayase though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:31.19,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so picky!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.35,0:20:32.96,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I got it.\NI'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.88,0:20:36.45,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Five minutes to detonation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:10.64,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The kid's really gotten good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.51,0:21:19.53,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:26.56,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,1st Lieutenant Hayase,\NI'm going to smash the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:27.96,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Please stand back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.13,0:21:30.18,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.75,0:21:34.64,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, now get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.00,0:21:38.00,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How could you do that to Riber's room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.07,0:21:38.88,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.26,0:21:40.34,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:41.70,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.80,0:21:44.02,intercom paging,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,One minute to detonation.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:49.04,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what happened here, but\NI risked my life to come get you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.47,0:21:50.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Leave me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.31,0:21:52.27,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:21:55.55,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No! Let me go!\NLet me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.51,0:22:00.48,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty seconds to detonation!\NAll units, fall back!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.27,0:22:03.79,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,RIBER!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.05,0:22:26.22,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.45,0:22:59.56,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Bastards! Damn!\NDammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.71,0:23:05.11,Macross1,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Still, things are starting to get interesting.\NAnd next time, I'll win!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:34.93,signM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\pos(58,107)}Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.06,0:23:34.93,signM,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\pos(302,469)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.48,0:23:39.71,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Lynn Minmay celebrates her sixteenth birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.97,0:23:42.61,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,On that same day, Hikaru is promoted\nto 2nd Lieutenant
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:46.62,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,and put in charge of two subordinates,\NMax and Kakizaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.92,0:23:49.79,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,However, the joy of this day is\Nshattered by a sudden attack
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:52.04,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,by Kamujin and his armored battalion.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:54.31,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Macross is once again\nplaced in deadly peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.91,0:23:58.33,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Super Dimension\NFortress Macross:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.58,0:24:02.04,signM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H00FF00&\pos(85,144)}LONGEST BIRTHDAY
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.45,0:24:00.57,narration,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,"LONGEST BIRTHDAY"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.23,0:24:22.92,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&}I won't follow it anymore,{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.14,0:24:29.63,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,, {\b1\c&HFF00FF&}The shadow you cast as you run away{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.81,0:24:36.15,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,, {\b1\c&HFF00FF&}We all keep running until the end{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.41,0:24:43.83,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,, {\b1\c&HFF00FF&}But we still can't see the goal{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.20,0:24:50.51,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&}What awaits us after today?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.90,0:24:56.54,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,, {\b1\c&HFF00FF&}What awaits us beyond tomorrow?{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.76,0:25:04.18,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&}Even now, I keep running toward{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.31,0:25:15.31,songM,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\c&HFF00FF&}The light that shines so far away{\b0}
